step 1: first create one folder ,,inside that folder  create 2 files 
1)docker-compose.yml
2)prometheus.yml

  Step 2:
  now open terminal note:docker desktop should be in open (start)
give this commands in vscode terminal
 1)docker compose up -d
  2) docker ps

step 3:
open browser 
1)  promethus:   http://localhost:9090
in promethus->status->target health   ->it will show some endpoints
2)grafana:  http://localhost:3000  
     in grafana->connection->datasource->prometheus->in last save and apply
        ->go to dashboard->import dashboard-> (Find and import dashboards for common applications at grafana.com/dashboards )-> give (1860)  
     then click load
then u can see a dashboard


